    "üìÅ 05 - Organizational Cyber (OUTPUT) ‚Üí #05-organizational_cyber/",
    "üìÅ 06 - Learning, Notes (OUTPUT) ‚Üí #06-learning_notes/",
    "üìÖ Changelog (OUTPUT) ‚Üí #changelog/",
    "üï∏Ô∏è UNSTRUCTURED (CAPTURE, WORK) ‚Üí #unstructured/",
