    "",
    "=== Tag Depth Nuance Issue ===",
    "IMPORTANT: There's a design question about tag depth:",
    "",
    "Scenario: File at `VaultUser1/üìÅ 01 - Projects/MyProject/note.md`",
    "",
    "Option A: Just the full path tag",
    "  Tags: #--vaultuser1/01-projects/myproject",
    "",
    "Option B: Entity + path tags",
    "  Tags: #--vaultuser1, #--vaultuser1/01-projects/myproject",
    "",
    "Option C: Entity + category + path tags",
    "  Tags: #--vaultuser1, #01-projects/myproject, #--vaultuser1/01-projects/myproject",
    "",
    "This nuance needs to be:",
    "1. Configurable per rule (option to add parent tags)",
    "2. Documented in TAG_DEPTH_NUANCE.md",
    "3. Testable in the test vault",
    "",
    "Current implementation: Option A (just full path)",
    "Recommended: Make this configurable",
    "",
    "See TAG_DEPTH_NUANCE.md for full technical discussion.",
    "",
    "=== Transformation Preferences ===",
    "Tags:",
    "- snake_case",
    "- Keep number prefixes (01, 02, etc.)",
